Happy Travel Life with BEOW From the day we were established, BEOW has stuck to our philosophy of designing, developing, and innovating new products for our customers, improving our products according to their feedback, and striving to provide better service and protection for our customers. We have an experienced and creative design team, and a production factory that meets modern quality requirements, so our suitcases are a combination of innovation and classics, and we will create better and stronger luggage for you!

How is the four-piece suitcase packaged and how many packages will I receive? 16-inch, 20-inch, 24-inch, and 28-inch suitcases can be nested within each other. One set will be packed in one box, please open the 28in luggage to check when receiving the package. How to reset the TSA lock? 1. The lock on the original position is 0-0-0. 2. Press the small round reset button using a pen or pencil. 3. Set the desired combination using the dials. 4. Press the side tab - you will hear a click, then the new lock set. Does each size have an expansion zipper? Only 24-inch and 28-inch have expansion zippers, which adds additional hardside luggage space capacity by 20%. What material of the suitcase? Is it easy to scratch? BEOW luggage set made from extra strong ABS material, which is lightweight and extremely durable. Features textured finish to prevent against scratches,keeping lightweight luggage set beautiful trip after trip. What should I do if there is an issue with the luggage sets? For any issues in product & servicing, please contact BEOW via the Amazon email of your order, or search " Beow Direct" on FB.

Happy with purchase there is no sign of wear and tear or any damage.Nicely packed and shipped. Colors and quality seems very good. Information they have provided are very useful, 16" bag size 13.18" L x 7.87" W x 18.5" H weight is 5 lbs, 20" Bag size 15.35" L x 9.05" W x 22.83" H weight is 6.28 Lbs, 24" bag size 17.32" x 10.51" W x 26.37" H weight is 8.15 lbs, 28" bag size 20.07" L x 12.2" W x 30.31" H weight is 9.81 lbs.4 piece luggage set - high quality. Nice thing is their wheels - 360 degree multi-directional 4 spinner wheels offer effortless mobility in any direction. Double wheel design is more durable.Also The side mounted TSA lock provides you with safety and security, which only you or a TSA agent have easily open hard case suitcases when traveling. reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It's what I wanted!
reviews.reviewText: 4 stars because I have not used it yet. Iike that this 4 piece luggage stores into one piece, it has the double 360 degree wheels, can be locked with TA access while traveling. And I like the green apple color for high visibility at luggage claim!

Just got these for a trip to Mexico. The 2 smaller ones could be used as carry on and the 2 larger would be for checked bags. Nice quality. We will see how they hold up to travel next week. I think they will be great.

Our luggage set just arrived and let me say, I’m impressed! It’s super cute and for the price; the quality seems great! They spin easily, zips open well, and over all; we’re excited to see how they hold up for our trip to Mexico!We purchased the “mint green” set.If you’re on the fence about these sets, DON’T HESITATE. 100% worth the money! 🙌🏼

We just got this set in and it looks good and solid and we love the colour! We got the mint set but it looks like a nice aqua colour. The two larger suitcases do have an extra zipper and are expandable (so maybe they have updated the suitcases since the reviews that said they aren't expandable as they are now). The material is hard and more matte than shiny. We noticed the box with the 3 suitcases in it was a bit heavy but individually the suitcases aren't too heavy. They roll well and the wheels seem good. The handles and locks and zippers seem pretty solid. We are going on a trip in 2 weeks so we will see how they hold up and update after the trip.

Just used 3 of the full set on 4 flights and they came out good. There are a couple of dings on them but that is to expected. We had no issues with them and I would recommend. Loved the colour too! Immediately recognized our cases.
Everything ok, nice quality for a nice price
